<div style="background-color: #fff; border-top: 1px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 1px solid #c4c4c4; padding: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: #f4f4f4 #e4e4e4 #c4c4c4 #e4e4e4;">
<h2>Save £50 per person on Winter Breaks in Northern Norway</h2>
<p class="p1">We’re pleased to be able to offer Silver Travel members and exclusive £50 per person discount on our range of short winter breaks in Northern Norway. To take advantage of this offer, <strong>simply book by 30 September 2016 quoting ‘Silver Travel’.</strong></p>
<p class="p2"> </p>
<p class="p3">Northern Norway has lots to offer. Discover the distinctive culture of the Sámi people, embark on a boat trip to go in search of whales, try your hand at husky-sledding or even get a ‘kiss’ from a wolf! You’ll be surrounded by stunning wilderness scenery and have the chance to witness the magical experience of watching the <a data-udi="umb://document/280ef861622541caa4a7e53db8f83271" href="/{localLink:umb://document/280ef861622541caa4a7e53db8f83271}" title="Northern Lights">Northern Lights</a>. Choose from 3 or 4 nights and <a data-udi="umb://document/336a323374f046cfa0591948e538170e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/336a323374f046cfa0591948e538170e}" title="Northern Fjord Norway">3 different itineraries</a>.</p>
<p class="p1">To book or find out more, see our <a data-udi="umb://document/5ae8c1cd62fc4f8b84b0a5d589f22287" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5ae8c1cd62fc4f8b84b0a5d589f22287}" title="Winter Breaks in Northern Norway">Northern Norway page</a>.</p>
<p class="p1"> </p>
<p class="p3">Terms and Conditions</p>
<ol class="ol1">
<li class="li3">1)<span class="Apple-tab-span"> </span>The £50 per person discount is valid for new bookings made direct with Inghams 24 August to 30 September 2016 on Inghams’ Winter Breaks in Northern Norway; the discount cannot be applied retrospectively but it can be used on top of any existing discounts.</li>
<li class="li3">2)<span class="Apple-tab-span"> </span>To obtain the discount you MUST quote Silver Travel at time of booking. Normal Inghams booking conditions apply. All holidays subject to availability.</li>
<li class="li3">3)<span class="Apple-tab-span"> </span>Inghams reserve the right to amend or remove this offer at any time without notice</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
